# Keep OS / editor cruft out of the published `npm pack` tarball.
# Exclude-only: everything else (Runtime/, Tests/, Samples~/, docs, and all .meta
# files Unity needs) is still packed.
.DS_Store
._*
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
*.swp
*.tmp
# `*~` drops editor backup files (e.g. Foo.cs~) but also matches the UPM
# `Samples~` and `Documentation~` directory names — re-include them so they are packed.
*~
!Samples~/
!Samples~/**
!Documentation~/
!Documentation~/**
